<h1>Band 5 nurse recruitment</h1>
<p>We know that you value working in an area you enjoy, in a position that fits your career plans.</p>
<p>So we have made our recruitment process easy to understand and use so you can start the job you have always dreamt of. We also have a dedicated nursing recruitment team to support you through every stage of the process</p>
<p>The Trust manages all Band 5 nurse recruitment centrally and holds a number of recruitment campaigns and <a href="">open days/job fairs</a> every year. Vacancies are divided into four staff groups – General, Theatre, Critical Care and Children’s – across all our sites.</p>
<p>These positions are not open to newly qualified nurses who are recruited to our <a href="">Preceptorship programme</a> training scheme through <a href="">dedicated campaigns.</a></p>
<p>Check our <a href="">current vacancies</a> for the latest nursing opportunities.</p>
