<dd>All inpatient and outpatient wards including Medicine, Surgery, Cardiac, Renal, Haematology/Chemotherapy, Neurosciences, Stroke, Emergency Department, Gynaecology, Liver, Day Surgery, Sexual Health, Ophthalmology, Dermatology, Radiology and Dialysis.</dd>
<dt>Theatre opportunities</dt>
<dd>All main theatres and day surgery (scrub, anaesthetics and recovery) including Endoscopy, Cardiac Catheter, Cardiac, Liver Transplant, Anaesthetics and Recovery.</dd>
<dt>Critical Care opportunities</dt>
<dd>Medical and Surgical ITU, Neuro HDU, Liver ITU, Cardiac Recovery/HDU, Coronary Care units, Cardiothoracic HDU.</dd>
<dt>Children’s opportunities</dt>
